{"tid":1458372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"散水計可中, 分化計點都唔中得!!","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:03.000Z","uid":78211,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9444613bad13311aa712e7315b2c48afc28dd87","tid":1458372,"uid":78211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"首先自首, 我係中左散水計嘅一份子, 要失望要屌可隨便<br />\n中計原因不多解釋, 已經有萬千個post 傾緊<br />\n<br />\n但希望大家失望完屌完之後可以重新團結返<br />\n散水一日唔會輸, 但如果因為呢次散水而分化嘅話就正中敵人下懷<br />\n我相信今日中計嘅手足都有相當嘅覺悟同愧疚<br />\n過咗去嘅彌補唔到, 但下次(聽日?)一定會做得更好更聰明<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都記得任何事都不割席不分化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4b8a96b21f1bf515f40edf23877d7cef3ab815","tid":1458372,"uid":78211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"自推, 只希望勿分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc2e78e09f0bfdb0dacc624b1d86a758a1eb878","tid":1458372,"uid":28005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68434649b742a5fb5f7a993732d330209e5ad86c","tid":1458372,"uid":78211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e8ff44389a2eaa0cec36ecaa7855671cb6772d","tid":1458372,"uid":272866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"e7669b998ca9c859bd09df536a6da2f67ffb221c","tid":1458372,"uid":78211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96e8ff44389a2eaa0cec36ecaa7855671cb6772d","tid":1458372,"uid":272866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}